      "x": "OTHER TOPICAL ANTIFUNGALS — the grab-bag. The lecture closes with a set of mostly topical agents to recognize by name rather than mechanism: ciclopirox (broad topical, also for nails), tolnaftate and naftifine and butenafine (topical tinea/athlete’s foot), haloprogin, and undecylenic acid (OTC athlete’s-foot preparations). These round out the dermatophyte/superficial toolkit and are not high-yield individually."
